{"tid":2424030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"暴雨後「黑蚊龍捲風」詭衝天際　嚇壞阿根廷民眾","createTime":"2021-02-26T09:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T10:33:26.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7acdc6ddece7a5f225d711da2b994d41e9d94cd4","tid":2424030,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:19:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k7OROBlgBtQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk7OROBlgBtQ&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=51a6a291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k7OROBlgBtQ</a><br />\n<br />\n阿根廷近日受到暴雨侵襲，當地民眾外出時目擊天空捲起許多道「深黑色龍捲風」從地上衝向天際，不過仔細一看才發現，這些龍捲風竟是由「蚊子」組成，數量多到形成龍捲風，特殊奇景嚇壞不少路過駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2021/02/25/19/39773550-9300919-image-m-16_1614282547167.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2021%2F02%2F25%2F19%2F39773550-9300919-image-m-16_1614282547167.jpg&h=8dfcd693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，位於阿根廷馬達里亞加（Madariaga）與皮納馬（Pinamar）間的74號公路，24日有駕駛發現路邊有一道道大型深色龍捲風，沒想到仔細看才發現，這並非天氣現象，而是由黑壓壓的「蚊子軍團」組成的「蚊柱」，讓目擊民眾驚呼「這龍捲風越來越大，以前從沒見過這種東西！」 <br />\n<br />\n事實上，在74號公路出現蚊子龍捲風前，阿根廷首都布宜諾斯艾利斯（Buenos Aires）就傳出遭到大批蚊蟲侵襲。寄生蟲與病媒研究中心（CEPAVE）研究員加西亞（Juan Jose Garcia）指出，因為連日暴雨造成洪水氾濫，這些積水導致雌性蚊蟲大量產卵，才會有此現象。 <br />\n<br />\n加西亞表示，這些蚊子不會對人類造成威脅，但有可能會干擾農業活動，15天後牠們就會開始死去。儘管如此，當地許多民眾仍呼籲政府以煙燻法殺死這大量的蚊子；阿根廷當局對此回應，煙燻法是無效的，僅能殺死部分蚊子，且有毒物質會進入食物鏈破壞生態，建議民眾這15天內做好防蚊措施即可。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/fun/1469311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Ffun%2F1469311&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=31d97873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/fun/1469311</a>"},{"pid":"03e87c2f8222aa23357573372924aa3b9cca1d1a","tid":2424030,"uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:20:00.000Z","msg":"好癢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8197cc7ac8ccba568d91a39902ecac1cd87ac0e","tid":2424030,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:21:34.000Z","msg":"一拳超人"},{"pid":"e4e7864fa34a1fd77a45a9797d911b8bdeaf0831","tid":2424030,"uid":52123,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i03piccdn.sogoucdn.com/12a645a3fc222dff\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi03piccdn.sogoucdn.com%2F12a645a3fc222dff&h=cf51f871&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93c46ebc7c27d1600580b8e999007c2449d00253","tid":2424030,"uid":299984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:24:00.000Z","msg":"黑旋風夠唒威 黑旋風的確好使"},{"pid":"5a2ae8b8e01e2a534ec81d68c80cda419153c667","tid":2424030,"uid":95519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x1Fm1q9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx1Fm1q9.jpg&h=e81292e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZq6s5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZq6s5w.jpg&h=4c3428b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"299ae5862e085ff8e4a6205d4bf2e32869fc704e","tid":2424030,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:32:04.000Z","msg":"用袋入住佢盡快拎去送俾中囯"},{"pid":"8a9b475e23ff9cd21e9677e9ece91a21c07ef66b","tid":2424030,"uid":68041,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"伊藤潤二<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/btj3vkQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbtj3vkQ.png&h=f0dd51da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"864e5f43b3d849590123f6dd486c11f5ff4671be","tid":2424030,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:36:25.000Z","msg":"一個人可以係入面頭到幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07858cf9c4044e4992e